1. Transmitted herewith is the Memorandum of Oral Commitment for
Mr. Alberto PONZOA y Alvarez (aka "Unio"
08
2. Subject was originally a contact of the Havana Station and in the summer
of 1960, using his best (EYRCS) made the first of four successful sea renderous
operations with MATUSA TIDF. He was subsequently forced to escape from
05 Cuba, in PISCIS is December 1960. Since this date Subject has a siald on many
maritime operations in WASP, MATUSA TIDF and on several Cuba-craved
boats. On several occasions he has effected rubber-bot beach landings to meet
reception parties under extremely hazardous circumstances.
3. In Mitaln Subject was associated with the AMBPS but has become
disenchanted with this group because of costant political squibbles and their
lack of ability to perform to his satisfaction. He now wishes to disassociate
himself completely from any Cuban political group and desires to place himself
under KUBARK coatrul.
4. Is it proposed to use Subject as a small boat captain in maritime
operations; as an intermediate craft crewman in beach landings; as interpreter
on American-crowd vessels; to assist in training Cuba, non-English-speaking
crews and to assist generally where and when needed.
